snippet.title: Metal Gear Cloud Finale - a "Rain on Your Parade" teaser
snippet.description:
Cloud? CLOOOOUUDD!!!!!
We're working on silly game where you play as a cloud and rain on people’s weddings and parades.


Follow development on:

Twitter:  https://twitter.com/unboundCreation
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/unboundcreations/
Website: http://unboundcreations.com/games/rain-on-your-parade/
